flowRoot.flowPara: Kitty is a Liverpool seamstress heading to Brooklyn to seek work. Her friend Smokey moved years ago and she has been lured by Smokey's letters.
She once worked as a charwoman for Lord Cheshire. Claims not to know that he is on board.
Donnie has been a steward with the Gurnard line for three years.
Over time he has become increasingly dissatisfied with the life and lack of prospects, and he is preparing to leave.
Has Donnie taken one last opportunity to line his pockets?
Calico is the housekeeper for Gurnard Lines' SS Atlantic.
She is liable to be frustrated about anything that interrupts getting her work done.
Pussy is a singer who is returning to New York from a European tour. The tour didn't go as well as she had hoped.
Rumour has it that Pussy has entertained the affections of some of London's most eligible batchelors.
Lord Cheshire is a wealthy bon-vivant, heading to New York on business. His charisma makes him a successful entrepreneur, though some say he is not so successful at the card table.
His reputation as a rake precede him. Has a jilted lover plotted against him?
The esteemed Doctor Manx chairs the Royal Ontological Society.
While he is highly intelligent, he carries himself with an aloofness that many find offputting.
Buster Baines is a Texan hotel magnate who has been in England looking for antiques with which to decorate a new hotel he is opening in Las Vegas.
Buster is direct and short of patience.
Katerina is a Spanish artist heading back to New York to paint.
